lih.kg/1242813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242813</a><br />\n<br />\n再玩膠，我地就會輸，唔好再俾膠post分散我地嘅注意力，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我推晒下面啲post上熱門！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">催淚彈、胡椒噴霧</span></span><br />\n發夢夢到幾個德國朋友教我點處理催淚彈 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1218344/page/1</a><br />\n[Gear撚] 催淚彈對防指南 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214624/page/1</a><br />\n［學術］中咗催淚彈同胡椒噴霧解決方法 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223200/page/1</a><br />\n[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴磅必須用品 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217785/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">裝備</span></span><br />\n&lt;抗爭手冊&gt; <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1085603/page/2</a><br />\n振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1224572/page/1</a><br />\n知己知彼 百戰百勝圖解香港警察裝備 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1206461/page/1</a><br />\n最近有個新喪屍GAME IDEA <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1222684/page/1</a><br />\n[突發] 621 雙方陣營裝備分析 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1240449/page/1</a><br />\n[魔防的重要性］所有人都要有足夠魔防 N95同泳鏡係最低要求 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242265/page/1</a><br />\n星期五嘅野餐行動 請現在立